tegration, the most interesting parst will be:\n\n  * LLM service\n  * Rewrite service\n\nEndpoint documentation is available at /docs when the application is running.\n\n## About\n\nA repository for refactored steer AI backend\n\nwww.steerapp.ai\n\n### Topics\n\nopenai fastapi\n\n### Resources\n\nReadme\n\nActivity\n\nCustom properties\n\n### Stars\n\n4 stars\n\n### Watchers\n\n1 watching\n\n### Forks\n\n0 forks\n\nReport repository\n\n## Releases\n\nNo releases published\n\n## Packages 0\n\nNo packages published\n\n## Languages\n\n  * Python 98.2%\n  * Dockerfile 1.8%\n\n## Footer\n\n\u00a9 2024 GitHub, Inc.\n\nYou can\u2019t perform that action at this time.\n\n", "frontpage": false}
